'''Hitec''' is a company based in [[South Korea]] that manufactures [[radio control]] devices, including [[transmitter]]s, [[receiver (radio)|receivers]], [[Servomechanism|servos]], electronics and [[model aircraft]]. Later products include [[robotics]], servos with [[Karbonite gears]] and the [[Robonova]]—a [[humanoid robot]] accepted in the [[Robo one]] [[robot competition]]. Hitec is linked to Multiplex USA.

