'''''How'd That Get On My Plate?''''' is a television series on [[Food Network]].

The show premiered in July 2008, and hosted by [[Sunny Anderson]]. The program investigates how various foods are produced (including [[honey]], [[milk]], [[egg (food)|eggs]], [[strawberries]], and [[Cocoa solids|cocoa]] in the first season), from their rawest form to their finished state, and features visits to food production factories throughout the [[United States]].

